## ğŸš€ Deployment (Free)

### Deploy to Vercel (5 minutes):
```bash
# Install Vercel CLI
npm i -g vercel

# Deploy
vercel

# Follow prompts, get your URL!
```

### Deploy to Netlify:
1. Push code to GitHub
2. Go to netlify.com
3. "New site from Git"
4. Select repo, click "Deploy"
5. Get your URL!

